<L>Compo&s;itum lecto &s;omnus te mollis eburno</L>
<L>Excipit, &amp; pict&acirc; &s;tragula ve&s;te tegunt;</L>
<L><PB REF="31">At mi&s;ero rector &s;uperum compellitur antro,</L>
<L>Nec quo fe&s;&s;a toro membra reponat, habet.</L>
<L>Et quem nulla capit &s;edes jam &s;ede moratur</L>
<L>Parva, ac in &s;tabulo maximus ho&s;pes ade&s;t:</L>
<L>Immolles Chri&s;to praebent prae&s;epia cunas,</L>
