<L>Hic pecudes, &s;tabulumque vides, &amp; vile mapale;</L>
<L>Sufficiunt cunis attamen i&s;ta &s;uis:</L>
<L>Nec &s;ua &s;trata nitent ullo cunabula cultu,</L>
<L>Sed vilem prae&s;tant &s;tramen &amp; herba torum:</L>
<L>In culmo &amp; palea merito puer i&s;te recumbens,</L>
<L>Frumentum populi cum foret ille &s;ui;</L>
<L>Affatuque bovis, &s;ociique fruetur a&s;elli;</L>
<L>Hac rerum Dominus frigora pellit ope.</L>
<L>Virgo, Dei mater, tu non palatia curas,</L>
