<L>Mille oculis puerum &s;pectant hunc &s;ydera nocte,</L>
<L>Candida (proh) paleae dum &s;ua membra premunt:</L>
<L>Ardent &s;e induere in paleas, &amp; cedere Coelo</L>
<L>Sydera, &s;ic membris e&s;&s;e beata &s;uis.</L>
