<DIV2>
<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><BIBL><HI>Joann. 19.</HI></BIBL>
<P>De Pa&s;&s;ione Domini no&s;tri Je&s;u Chri&s;ti.</P></Q>
</EPIGRAPH>
<L>Currite nunc rivi, lachrymaeque per ora volutae,</L>
<L>Currite, largifluo mergite fonte genas.</L>
<L>Tri&s;tia flebilibus re&s;onant nunc &s;ata quaerelis,</L>
<L>Lucti&s;onis etiam currat arena modis.</L>
<L><PB REF="33">Quis modo non doleat, gemebundo pectore plangat,</L>
<L>Commemorans Domini tri&s;tia fata &s;ui.</L>
<L>Pro nobis &s;olum de&s;cendit Chri&s;tus ad ima,</L>
